verbose_text: Consistent with the neurosphere size results, ZIKV infection dramatically reduced cell viability and treatment of cilengitide, alphavbeta5 blocking Ab, or SB273005 reversed this effect in both neurospheres produced from human induced pluripotent stem cell (iPSC)-derived NSCs (ihNSC) (XREF_FIG) and human fetal derived primary NSCs (hfNSC) (XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY).
